'''热带风暴贝里尔'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Beryl}}）是有纪录以来最强烈的一个在[[淡季大西洋热带风暴列表|淡季]]形成、并曾[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = John L. Beven II | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Tropical Cyclone Report | date = 2012-12-12 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131204044941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL022012_Beryl.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL022012_Beryl.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-12-04 }}</ref>。<!-- the 1908 hurricane made a direct hit, not landfall, and Beryl had 65 mph (105 km/h) sustained winds at landfall, making it the strongest U.S. landfall for any preseason or postseason storm -->系统源于5月26日[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海的一片[[低气压|低气压天气系统]]，起初属[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]，之后因行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]升高，并且[[风切变|垂直风切变]]逐渐减少而缓慢发展出热带天气系统特征。5月27日晚，气旋在距[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]北部不足190公里洋面转变成[[2012年大西洋飓风季|2012年大西洋飓风季]]的第2个热带气旋。次日清晨，贝里尔以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里的最高强度从佛罗里达州[[杰克逊维尔海滩_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔海滩]]附近登岸。风暴很快减弱成热带低气压，在缓慢行经[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]期间降下倾盆大雨。受[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响，气旋转向东北，于5月30日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

贝里尔尚处亚热带气旋阶段时就在古巴降下暴雨，引发多起洪灾和[[泥石流|泥石流]]，导致两人丧生。佛罗里达州南部和巴哈马同样受到倾盆大雨的影响。成为热带气旋后，风暴产生的大浪对美国东南海岸沿线造成冲击，[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]的[[富丽海滩_(南卡罗莱纳州)|富丽海滩]]有1人失踪。贝里尔登陆佛罗里达州期间产生狂风，导致约3万8000人失去供电。大量降水缓解当地旱情的同时，也帮助扑灭了气旋沿途的许多山火。南卡罗莱纳州[[奥兰治堡县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|奥兰治堡县]]有1名男子被倒塌的树木砸死。贝里尔还在北卡罗莱纳州东南部催生出[[改良藤田级数|改良藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|EF}}1级的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，[[加特利县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|加特利县]][[佩莱蒂耶_(北卡罗莱纳州)|佩莱蒂耶]]有部分树木被刮断，数十套民宅受损。风暴总体导致的损失数额不高，估计只有14万8000美元（2012年[[美元|美元]]）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Beryl 2012 track.png}}
5月16日，[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]上空发展出[[低压槽|低压槽]]。系统向东飘流并进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西北部，于5月18日催生出[[低气压|低气压区]]。接下来3天里，低气压区基本没有移动，也没有出现发展，直至5月22日开始向东北方向移动时结构才有所改善。<ref name="tcr" />5月23日，细长的低气压区内已经存在杂乱无章的[[对流|对流]]区。途经古巴[[青年岛|青年岛]]期间，当地强烈的[[风切变|风切变]]令系统中存在的环流中心暴露在外，对流持续也非常短暂。<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | author2 = Robbie Berg | date = 2012-05-23 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120530040442/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205231822.txt | archivedate = 2012-05-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205231822.txt | format = TXT }}</ref>次日，系统经过[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]<ref name="tcr" />，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为，低气压区途经海域接下来两天的环境会有利于热带气旋形成<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | author2 = Robbie Berg | date = 2012-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120530040447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205241239.txt | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205241239.txt | archivedate = 2012-05-30 | format = TXT }}</ref>。随着云层格局逐渐聚拢，低气压的结构得到改善。接下来24小时里，系统继续深入西大西洋，还有从[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]延伸到[[古巴|古巴]]上空的对流[[雨带|带]]将环流西南边缘包裹起来<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | author2 = James Franklin | date = 2012-05-24 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205241654.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120530041052/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205241654.txt | archivedate = 2012-05-30 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Todd Kimberlain | author2 = Stacy Stewart | date = 2012-05-24 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205250037.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120530041057/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2012/TWOAT.201205250037.txt | archivedate = 2012-05-30 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-26 | author = Mike Formosa | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201114941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2012/TWDAT.201205260004.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2012/TWDAT.201205260004.txt | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-01 }}</ref>。5月25日，系统与[[冷心低壓|中到上层低气压]]相互影响，中心因此进一步向东北方向偏离。系统中心附近风力达到[[烈風|烈風]]强度，并且对流的组织结构已有足够改善，<ref name="tcr" />美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月26日凌晨3点将位于[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]以东约490公里洋面的气旋归类为亚热带风暴贝里尔并开始发布公告<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Todd Kimberlain | date = 2012-05-26 | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | title = Subtropical Storm Beryl Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-07-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150707043600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.001.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过飓风季过后的重新分析结果表明，贝里尔在3小时前就已发展成形<ref name="tcr" />。

[[File:Beryl_May_25_2012_2245Z.png|thumb]]

贝里尔成形后，[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]上空逐渐消退的低压槽令外部环境有弱转向趋势。气象部门预计，由于水温升幅有限，还有干燥空气的不利影响，风暴不大可能出现显著强化<ref name="disc1" />，5月26日当天其对流一直很少。当晚，贝里尔受逐渐形成的高压脊影响开始稳步向西南方向移动<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-26 | title = Subtropical Storm Beryl Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = John Cangialosi | author2 = James Franklin | accessdate = 2015-09-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.003.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710074431/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。到这个时候，气旋的下层环流中心已经和上层中心在垂直方向对齐<ref name="tcr" />。风暴中心附近的大气环境变得更加潮湿，行经洋面水温也有提高，对流因此出现增长<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Subtropical Storm Beryl Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Jack Beven | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.005.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710085424/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。5月27日，贝里尔开始转变成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Subtropical Storm Beryl Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Daniel Brown | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710060023/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.007.shtml? | author2 = John Cangialosi | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，并于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天18点完成转变<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel Brown | author2 = John Cangialosi | date = 2012-05-27 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Public Advisory Seven-A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710072902/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.public_a.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.public_a.007.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴结构在逼近[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]期间得到改善，中心周围雨带中的对流有所增长<ref name="8disc">{{cite report | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Daniel Brown | author2 = John Cangialosi | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.008.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710072438/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 }}</ref>。5月27日晚，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]测得的飞行高速层风速为每小时148公里，表明贝里尔的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]为每小时110公里，这也是该气旋达到的最高强度<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Lixion Avila | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.009.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710113511/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.009.shtml | author2 = Todd Kimberlain | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。但从多普勒雷达的数据来看，风暴有可能在5月27日晚短暂达到飓风强度标准，只是飓风季过后的分析认为这些数据尚不足以得出确定性结论<ref name="tcr" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}5月28日凌晨4点10分左右，贝里尔经小幅减弱后以风力时速约105公里强度从佛罗里达州[[杰克逊维尔海滩_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔海滩]]附近登陆<ref name="land">{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710053644/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.update.05280415.shtml | author2 = Dave Roberts | date = 2012-05-28 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Tropical Cyclone Update | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.update.05280415.shtml? | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref><ref name="tcr" />。

气旋登陆后迅速减弱成热带低气压，前进速度也因北面的高压脊逐渐减弱而放缓，并于5月29日受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响转向北上，然后又转朝东北方向移动<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Tropical Depression Beryl Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Lixion Avila | author2 = John Cangialosi | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710115041/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.011.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref><ref name="fourteen">{{cite report | date = 2012-05-29 | title = Tropical Depression Beryl Discussion Fourteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = James Franklin | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710070802/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.014.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.014.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。虽已深入内陆，但贝里尔仍然保有足够对流，得以保持热带气旋状态<ref name="fourteen" />。5月30日逼近大西洋后，风暴中心以南和以东的对流有所增长，但由于有干燥空气入侵，气旋的卫星图像模糊不清<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-30 | title = Tropical Depression Beryl Discussion Eighteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Jack Beven | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.018.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710035043/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。根据多艘船只的观测报告，美国国家飓风中心于5月30日将接近南卡罗莱纳州海岸线的贝里尔升级成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" />。逐渐逼近的冷锋令系统加速向东北方向前进，环流变得拉长，关联对流也向北侧分散，表明贝里尔正在转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-30 | title = Tropical Depression Beryl Discussion Nineteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Lixion Avila | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710103356/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.019.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.019.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。到了5月30日晚，系统已完成转变，美国国家飓风中心因此发布针对贝里尔的最后一份公告<ref>{{cite report | date = 2012-05-30 | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Beryl Discussion Twenty | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = John Cangialosi | author2 = James Franklin | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710110912/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.020.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.discus.020.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。温带气旋继续向东北方向前进，之后转向[[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]。6月2日，贝里尔的残留在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南方向海域被更大规模的温带风暴吸收<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施、影响和纪录 ==
贝里尔以风力时速105公里强度登陆杰克逊维尔海滩，这一强度在所有登陆过美国、并且不是在大西洋飓风季正式时间段内形成的热带气旋中创下新纪录<ref name="tcr" />。贝里尔也是[[2012年大西洋飓风季|2012年大西洋飓风季]]正式开始前形成的第2场热带风暴，自1851年开始有纪录以来，这种情况还只发生过4次，另外3次分别是[[1887年大西洋飓风季|1887年]]、[[1908年大西洋飓风季|1908年]]和[[1951年大西洋飓风季|1951年]]<ref name="mailonline">{{cite web | date = 2012-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | title = Memorial Day is soaked and thousands lose power after Tropical Storm Beryl becomes strongest May cyclone to hit in more than a century with winds of up to 70mph | publisher = Mail Online | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120818131305/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2150649/Tropical-Storm-Beryl-hits-Florida-70mph-winds-rain-ruin-Memorial-Day-2012.html | archivedate = 2012-08-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2150649/Tropical-Storm-Beryl-hits-Florida-70mph-winds-rain-ruin-Memorial-Day-2012.html }}</ref><ref name="miamiherald">{{cite web |date=2012-05-31 |accessdate=2013-01-03 |title=Storm season off to a fast start |publisher=The Miami Herald |archivedate=2013-01-03 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2012/05/31/2826435/storm-season-off-to-a-fast-start.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DOA1ieoY?url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2012/05/31/2826435/storm-season-off-to-a-fast-start.html }}</ref>。

=== 古巴和巴哈马 ===
