贝尔里在成为热带气旋前就给[[古巴|古巴]]带去暴雨，其中又以[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]情况严重<ref name="fn">{{cite web | url = http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/05/25/hurricane-warning-issued-for-mexico-ahead-bud/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120809124554/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/05/25/hurricane-warning-issued-for-mexico-ahead-bud/ | title = Hurricane Bud roars toward Mexican coast | date = 2012-05-25 | work = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = [[福斯新闻频道|Fox News]] | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2012-08-09 }}</ref>，最高降雨量达557毫米<ref name="tcr" />。大量降水引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，迫使8500人离开家园<ref name="twdisc">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201114941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2012/TWDAT.201205260004.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2012/TWDAT.201205260004.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | author = Mike Formosa | date = 2012-05-26 | work = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="efe526" />。有两人因试图穿过泛滥的河流而遇难，洪灾令1109户民宅受损，另有47套被毁<ref name="afpes">{{cite news |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=2012-05-28 |title=Intensas lluvias dejan dos muertos y miles de casas dañadas en Cuba |publisher=El Nuevo Herald |accessdate=2013-01-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130122094947/http://www.elnuevoherald.com/2012/05/28/1214116/intensas-lluvias-dejan-dos-muertos.html |archivedate=2013-01-22 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.elnuevoherald.com/2012/05/28/1214116/intensas-lluvias-dejan-dos-muertos.html }}</ref>。虽然降雨致使大面积农田被淹，但也缓解了该国部分地区的旱情，为水库带去宝贵的雨水<ref name="efe526">{{cite news | agency = EFE | title = Evalúan daños en Cuba tras intensas lluvias | publisher = Primerahora.com | accessdate = 2012-05-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120531205502/http://www.primerahora.com/evaluandanosencubatrasintensaslluvias-652604.html | date = 2012-05-26 | url = http://www.primerahora.com/evaluandanosencubatrasintensaslluvias-652604.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-05-31 }}</ref>。

风暴的雷暴带和雨带进入巴哈马上空并降下暴雨，[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]的[[弗里波特_(巴哈马)|弗里波特]]（{{lang|en|Freeport}}）降下250毫米雨量<ref name="twdisc" />，[[新普罗维登斯岛|新普罗维登斯岛]]的低洼地区出现洪灾<ref name="ng">{{cite news | title = Weather system could become tropical storm as it leaves the Bahamas | date = 2012-05-26 | author = Taneka Thompson | newspaper = The Nassau Guardian | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150204195807/http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=31253&Itemid=27 | archivedate = 2015-02-04 | url = http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=31253&Itemid=27 }}</ref>。墨菲镇居民报告有龙卷风着陆，导致供电和电话线缆中断，多辆汽车被掀翻，3幢建筑物的屋顶受损<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=31252&Itemid=27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150204195810/http://www.thenassauguardian.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=31252&Itemid=27 | title = NEMA assesses damage after reported tornado in Abaco | date = 2012-05-26 | author = Taneka Thompson | newspaper = The Nassau Guardian | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-02-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。气旋产生的降水还对[[贝里群岛|贝里群岛]]、[[阿巴科群岛|阿巴科群岛]]、[[比米尼群岛|比米尼群岛]]以及另外多个小群岛构成影响<ref name="ng" />。

=== 佛罗里达州 ===
[[File:Beryl_2012_rainfall.png|thumb]]

贝里尔成为热带气旋前就在南佛罗里达产生局部暴雨，[[迈亚密国际机场|迈亚密国际机场]]测得250毫米雨量<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2101 | title = Invest 94L bringing heavy rains; Bud finally strengthening | author = Jeff Masters | date = 2012-05-23 | publisher = Weather Underground | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906074956/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2101 | archivedate = 2015-09-06 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 }}</ref>。这个数字创下该监测站5月测得的第2高单日雨量纪录<ref>{{cite journal | page = 7 | publisher = United States Department of Agriculture | date = 2012-05-30 | accessdate = 2012-10-29 | title = Weekly Weather and Crop Bulletin | volume = 99 | number = 22 | url = http://usda01.library.cornell.edu/usda/waob/weather_weekly//2010s/2012/weather_weekly-05-31-2012.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-10-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121029015954/http://usda01.library.cornell.edu/usda/waob/weather_weekly//2010s/2012/weather_weekly-05-31-2012.pdf | journal =  }}</ref>。降雨引起大范围街道洪灾，特别是[[斯威特沃特_(佛罗里达州)|斯威特沃特]]和[[多拉_(佛罗里达州)|多拉]]情况严重，许多司机被困，下班交通高峰也受到影响。[[迈阿密戴德学院|迈阿密戴德学院]]被迫取消5月23日早上的课程。<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-05-23 | title = Rains bring flooding to South Florida | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/local/21007541472183/rains-bring-flooding-to-south-florida/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130523121518/http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/local/21007541472183/rains-bring-flooding-to-south-florida | date = 2012-05-23 | publisher = WSVN News | accessdate = 2013-05-23 }}</ref>

针对贝里尔发布首份热带气旋公告时，美国国家飓风中心也向佛罗里达州[[布里瓦德县_(佛罗里达州)|布里瓦德县]]和[[沃卢西亚县|沃卢西亚县]]到南卡罗莱纳州[[艾迪斯托海滩_(南卡罗莱纳州)|艾迪斯托海滩]]之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，还向北至南卡罗莱纳州[[桑蒂河|桑蒂河]]（{{lang|en|Santee River}}）河口之间地区发布热带风暴观察预警<ref>{{cite web | author = Todd Kimberlain | date = 2012-05-26 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | title = Subtropical Storm Beryl Public Advisory One | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.public.001.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710053350/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/al02/al022012.public.001.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，当地的爵士音乐节和[[亡兵纪念日|亡兵纪念日]]活动被迫提早结束<ref name="msnbc527">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530123640/http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/05/27/11904742-tropical-storm-beryl-moves-ashore-in-northeast-florida |agency=Associated Press |publisher=MSNBC |date=2012-05-27 |title=Tropical Storm Beryl moves ashore in northeast Florida |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archivedate=2012-05-30 |deadurl=no |url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2012/05/27/11904742-tropical-storm-beryl-moves-ashore-in-northeast-florida }}</ref>。贝里尔登陆后，杰克逊维尔周边机场只有[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]和[[达美航空|达美航空]]的航班没有全部取消<ref name="afp528" />。

[[戴通纳海滩|戴通纳海滩]]有1名少年因遭遇大浪而丧生<ref>{{cite news | publisher = WESH Orlando | date = 2012-05-29 | title = Surf Off Central Fla. Coast Still Dangerous Today | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-09-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140903144651/http://www.wesh.com/Surf-Off-Central-Fla-Coast-Still-Dangerous-Today/14348750 | url = http://www.wesh.com/Surf-Off-Central-Fla-Coast-Still-Dangerous-Today/14348750 }}</ref>。因大浪和[[离岸流|离岸流]]的威胁，当地救生员限制人们下海游泳<ref name="msnbc527" />。[[费南迪纳比奇_(佛罗里达州)|费南迪纳比奇]]出现的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]最高，有1.14米<ref name="tcr" />。风暴登陆后在沿海地区产生强风，其中杰克逊维尔的胡格诺公园风速达到每小时87公里，附近的巴克岛则测得117公里的阵风时速<ref name="jaxpre">{{cite report |author=Al Sandrik |date=2012-06-01 |title=Post Tropical Cyclone Report... Tropical Storm Beryl... Updated |publisher=Jacksonville, Florida National Weather Service |accessdate=2012-06-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/687iOc2HH?url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS |archivedate=2012-06-02 |deadurl=yes |url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS&issuedby=JAX&product=PSH&format=CI&version=1&glossary=1 }}</ref>。受大风影响，[[马修斯大桥|马修斯大桥]]和万德伍德大桥被迫封闭<ref name="jaxpre" /><ref>{{cite news | publisher = News4Jax.com | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Heavy winds, rain bring storm damage, power outages | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-09-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140903133515/http://www.news4jax.com/news/Heavy-winds-rain-bring-storm-damage-power-outages-Mathews-Bridge-closed/14238240 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.news4jax.com/news/Heavy-winds-rain-bring-storm-damage-power-outages-Mathews-Bridge-closed/14238240 }}</ref>。多条输电线缆中断，导致杰克逊维尔市内有约3万8000居民家中停电<ref name="afp528">{{cite news |deadurl=yes |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=2012-05-28 |title=Tropical Storm Beryl lashes southeast US coast |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918125236/http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/World/Story/A1Story20120528-348959.html |url=http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest+News/World/Story/A1Story20120528-348959.html |publisher=AsiaOne |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archivedate=2015-09-18 }}</ref>。杰克逊维尔的霍根斯溪沿岸地区受到山洪爆发影响，大浪还令海堤和部分码头受损，一幢共管公寓和三辆汽车进水。[[129号美国国道|129号美国国道]]位于[[萨旺尼县_(佛罗里达州)|萨旺尼县]]境内部分路段被山洪淹没。<ref name="jaxpre" />整个杰克逊维尔遭受的破坏估计价值为2万美元<ref name="ncdc">{{cite journal |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |volume=54 |number=5 |title=Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena with Late Reports and Corrections |accessdate=2012-08-31 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AJfpU0Jn?url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-547FCD37-54A7-4A0E-B003-4396398C2C17.pdf |archivedate=2012-08-31 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-547FCD37-54A7-4A0E-B003-4396398C2C17.pdf |format=PDF |journal= }}</ref>。贝里尔的外围环流在杰克逊维尔以南的[[圣露西港_(佛罗里达州)|圣露西港]]催生出一场[[改良藤田级数|改良藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|EF}}0的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，其持续时间很短，只对两户民房构成轻度破坏<ref>{{cite report |author=Spratt |date=2012-05-31 |title=Post Tropical Cyclone Report... Tropical Storm Beryl |publisher=Melbourne, Florida National Weather Service |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archivedate=2012-05-31 |url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS&issuedby=MLB&product=PSH&format=CI&version=1&glossary=1 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/685C4HOEZ?url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS |display-authors=etal |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。估计这场龙卷风一共造成了2万美元损失<ref name="ncdc" />。另据报道，[[岩克镇_(佛罗里达州)|岩克镇]]也出现龙卷风<ref name="tcr" />。 气旋的移动速度缓慢，佛罗里达州因此普降暴雨，萨旺尼县的威尔伯恩（{{lang|en|Wellborn}}）降雨量达到最高的380毫米<ref name="rain">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | date = 2012-06-12 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl – May 23–30, 2012 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/beryl2012.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210064110/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/beryl2012.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-02-10 }}</ref>。威尔伯恩以南不远处的[[泰勒县_(佛罗里达州)|泰勒县]]境内一辆汽车在被淹的公路上打滑，撞到一位骑摩托车的男子头部导致伤重不治<ref>{{cite news | title = Godby Graduate Dies From Motorcycle Accident | last = Floyd | first = Joshua | location = [[塔拉赫西|Tallahassee, FL]] | date = 2012-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.wctv.tv/home/headlines/Godby_Graduate_Dies_From_Motorcycle_Accident_155167275.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140903104605/http://www.wctv.tv/home/headlines/Godby_Graduate_Dies_From_Motorcycle_Accident_155167275.html | station = WCTV | archivedate = 2014-09-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。据一线响应人员反映，由于能见度太差，他们花了20分钟时间才检查完约16公里道路。[[盖恩斯维尔_(佛罗里达州)|盖恩斯维尔]]在5月28日测得83毫米降水，创下单日降雨量的新纪录。<ref name="cnn">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | author = Ashley Hayes | date = 2012-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | title = Rainmaker Beryl poses flood threat in South | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2012/05/29/us/weather-beryl/index.html | archivedate = 2013-01-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130126190918/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/05/29/us/weather-beryl/index.html }}</ref>[[布鲁克斯–坦帕湾地区机场|赫尔南多县]]机场在5月29日测得93毫米降水，也刷新了单日降雨量纪录<ref>{{cite news | author = Danny Valentine | title = Tropical Depression Beryl dumps record rain in parts of Hernando County | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605090847/http://www.tampabay.com/news/weather/tropical-depression-beryl-dumps-record-rain-in-parts-of-hernando-county/1232584 | archivedate = 2015-06-05 | deadurl = no | date = 2012-05-30 | newspaper = Tampa Bay Times | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.tampabay.com/news/weather/tropical-depression-beryl-dumps-record-rain-in-parts-of-hernando-county/1232584 }}</ref>。北佛罗里达州的25处山火有80%被降雨扑灭。[[莱维县_(佛罗里达州)|莱维县]]出现[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]，于登岸后消散<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Ocala.com | author = Joe Callahan | title = Beryl quenches area wildfires | date = 2012-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.ocala.com/article/20120529/ARTICLES/120529691 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605073800/http://www.ocala.com/article/20120529/ARTICLES/120529691 | archivedate = 2015-06-05 }}</ref>。[[西特拉斯县|西特拉斯县]]有多户民宅被雨水淹没，损失数额约有10万8000美元<ref name="ncdc" />。

=== 乔治亚州、南卡罗莱纳州和北卡罗莱纳州 ===
5月27日，风暴登陆数小时前，[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[坎伯兰岛|坎伯兰岛]]官员下令所有在岛上露营的人员撤离<ref name="msnbc527" />。虽然风暴是在佛罗里达州登陆，但产生的风暴潮还是导致[[康登县_(乔治亚州)|康登县]][[圣玛丽斯_(乔治亚州)|圣玛丽斯]]（{{lang|en|St. Marys}}）部分地区被淹。该州降雨量最高的是康登县[[县城|县城]][[伍德拜恩_(乔治亚州)|伍德拜恩]]（{{lang|en|Woodbine}}），达179毫米。<ref name="jaxpre" />虽有引发轻度洪灾，但贝里尔的降水有利于缓解旱情<ref>{{cite news | author = Russ Bynum | agency = Associated Press | date = 2012-05-29 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | publisher = Boston Globe | archivedate = 2015-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605084807/http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2012/05/29/us_officials_assess_storm_preparations_after_beryl/?page=2 | title = US officials assess storm preparations after Beryl | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2012/05/29/us_officials_assess_storm_preparations_after_beryl/?page=2 }}</ref>。乔治亚州海岸沿线阵风时速最高的是[[杰基尔岛|杰基尔岛]]（{{lang|en|Jekyll Island}}），达到89公里<ref name="jaxpre" />，州内大范围地区风速达到热带风暴强度<ref name="tcr" />。[[麦金托什县_(乔治亚州)|麦金托什县]]有两套民宅因树木倒塌受损<ref>{{cite news | author = Russ Bynum | newspaper = The Virginian Pilot | date = 2012-05-29 | title = Most of Beryl's damage was to Memorial Day plans | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://hamptonroads.com/2012/05/tropical-storm-beryl-brings-wind-rain-florida | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150918140344/http://hamptonroads.com/2012/05/tropical-storm-beryl-brings-wind-rain-florida | archivedate = 2015-09-18 }}</ref>，[[奥兰治堡县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|奥兰治堡县]]一名正驾车在州高速公路上行驶的男子被倒塌的树木砸死<ref>{{cite news |publisher=WRDW-TV Augusta |date=2012-05-31 |title=1 man died in wreck as Beryl moved through SC |agency=Associated Press |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130209133658/http://www.wrdw.com/news/headlines/1_man_dies_in_wreck_as_Beryl_moved_through_SC_155964665.html?ref=665 |archivedate=2013-02-09 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-09-18 |url=http://www.wrdw.com/news/headlines/1_man_dies_in_wreck_as_Beryl_moved_through_SC_155964665.html?ref=665 }}</ref>，这也是风暴直接造成的唯一一起人员丧生事件，另外几起均属间接导致<ref name="tcr" />。南卡罗莱纳州的最强阵风时速出现在约翰逊堡，有74公里，该州近海还出现过更强的风速。[[杰斯帕县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|杰斯帕县]]的降雨量达到152毫米，是该州降水最多的所在。受大浪影响，[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]港有一艘船只沉没，船员幸得[[美国海岸警卫队|海岸警卫队]]救援<ref>{{cite report |author=RM |date=2012-06-01 |title=Post Tropical Cyclone Report... Tropical Storm Beryl |publisher=Charleston, South Carolina National Weather Service |accessdate=2012-06-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/687i0i4yW?url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS |display-authors=etal |deadurl=yes |url=http://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=NWS&issuedby=CHS&product=PSH&format=CI&version=1&glossary=1 |archivedate=2012-06-02 }}</ref>。[[富丽海滩_(南卡罗莱纳州)|富丽海滩]]有一人在游泳时遇上大浪而失踪<ref>{{cite news | publisher = WISTV10 | date = 2012-05-27 | title = Crews seek swimmer in rough SC surf | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120530074546/http://www.wistv.com/story/18635335/crews-seek-swimmer-in-rough-sc-surf | url = http://www.wistv.com/story/18635335/crews-seek-swimmer-in-rough-sc-surf | archivedate = 2012-05-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但没有计入死亡人数<ref name="tcr" />。贝里尔加速向东北方向行进后，南、北卡罗莱纳州降下暴雨，[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]出现局部洪灾。气旋在更北面的[[加特利县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|加特利县]]佩莱蒂耶（{{lang|en|Peletier}}）催生出改良藤田级数为{{lang|en|EF}}1级的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，摧毁了3套民宅，另有67套受损<ref>{{cite news | author = Bruce Smith | agency = Associated Press | date = 2012-05-30 | title = Tornado from remnants of Beryl destroy homes in NC | url = http://news.yahoo.com/tornado-remnants-beryl-destroy-homes-nc-205250877.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130410020220/http://news.yahoo.com/tornado-remnants-beryl-destroy-homes-nc-205250877.html | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | archivedate = 2013-04-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Kennedy | author2 = King | date = 2012-05-30 | title = Public Information Statement... Updated | publisher = Newport/Morehead City, North Carolina National Weather Service | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/Text/pns053012.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018194616/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/Text/pns053012.txt | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-18 }}</ref>。风暴的水分继续向北扩散，一直进入[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]和[[西弗吉尼亚州|西弗吉尼亚州]]境内<ref name="ncdc" />。

